317
00:32:17,560 --> 00:32:20,730
Shouldn't she be a boy?

318
00:32:20,730 --> 00:32:23,890
Xuan Nu always called her her son.

319
00:32:24,930 --> 00:32:27,040
I thought...

320
00:32:27,040 --> 00:32:30,860
No, she's a girl.

321
00:32:31,420 --> 00:32:37,080
It must be because Xuan Nu wanted a son to succeed Second Older Brother's Winged Monarch position,

322
00:32:37,080 --> 00:32:39,520
she called her that way.

323
00:32:47,960 --> 00:32:52,710
Xuan Nu had always been deceiving others and herself all her life.

324
00:33:00,300 --> 00:33:05,610
Have... you been at Kunlun Void all these years?

325
00:33:08,430 --> 00:33:11,600
Yes. Always.

326
00:33:11,600 --> 00:33:13,630
I've never left.

327
00:33:16,330 --> 00:33:19,210
I heard your teacher had returned.

328
00:33:19,210 --> 00:33:23,390
Did he blame you for refining a medicinal pill for me?

329
00:33:25,120 --> 00:33:26,930
No.

330
00:33:28,380 --> 00:33:32,440
Then, how about your fellow disciples. Did they make things hard for you because of me?

331
00:33:33,380 --> 00:33:35,470
Never.

332
00:33:38,490 --> 00:33:40,590
Then I can rest assured.

333
00:33:41,500 --> 00:33:43,420
I'll be taking my leave.

334
00:33:50,330 --> 00:33:52,260
Wait!

335
00:34:06,640 --> 00:34:09,480
After all, this is my Kunlun Void.

336
00:34:09,920 --> 00:34:12,190
Don't come again in the future.

337
00:34:12,950 --> 00:34:14,910
Don't come

338
00:34:16,630 --> 00:34:18,950
to look for me again.

339
00:34:23,010 --> 00:34:24,870
Sure.

340
00:34:35,320 --> 00:34:37,330
Goodbye.

341
00:35:44,660 --> 00:35:46,760
Teacher, you're back.

342
00:35:48,420 --> 00:35:52,290
