343
00:35:55,640 --> 00:35:57,540
He's awake.

344
00:35:57,540 --> 00:36:01,280
That's great. Seventeenth can finally get married.

345
00:36:53,000 --> 00:36:55,270
Play properly.

346
00:36:55,270 --> 00:37:00,150
Your father told me you must win 7 times against me or you can't go find him.

347
00:37:00,150 --> 00:37:03,330
How can I win against you?

348
00:37:03,330 --> 00:37:06,840
It's fine. I'll let you win.

349
00:37:12,250 --> 00:37:15,400
Your father cares about women too much.

350
00:37:15,850 --> 00:37:17,950
Let's stop playing. Let's stop playing.

351
00:37:17,950 --> 00:37:21,990
How about this? I'll tell you stories about your mother's childhood,

352
00:37:21,990 --> 00:37:25,170
or about your parent's love-hate relationship?

353
00:37:25,170 --> 00:37:27,780
How can my parents have a love-hate relationship?

354
00:37:27,780 --> 00:37:30,210
They only have great tenderness between lovers.

355
00:37:30,210 --> 00:37:31,810
Fine, okay.

356
00:37:31,810 --> 00:37:36,300
In Four Seas and Eight Wildernesses, only your parents have the greatest love.

357
00:37:36,300 --> 00:37:39,960
Then let's talk about your mother's childhood stories. Okay.

358
00:37:41,130 --> 00:37:44,590
Where should we start, Zhen Zhen?

359
00:37:44,590 --> 00:37:50,120
Just start from when his mother was 20,000 years old, she wandered around the Four Seas with me and caused troubles.

360
00:37:50,120 --> 00:37:53,510
We can talk till Mochi's younger sibling is born.

361
00:37:53,510 --> 00:37:56,320
Your mother was naughty when she was a child.

362
00:37:56,320 --> 00:37:58,060
She caused trouble every day.

363
00:37:58,060 --> 00:37:59,950
She actually went around taking other's items.

364
00:37:59,950 --> 00:38:03,880
She even forgot to return everything she took from others.

365
00:38:03,880 --> 00:38:06,450
Your mother was...

366
00:38:10,830 --> 00:38:12,660
Ye Hua.

367
00:38:15,720 --> 00:38:20,160
I've constantly dreamed about you these past three years.

368
00:38:20,970 --> 00:38:24,630
I couldn't separate my dreams from reality.

369
00:38:25,290 --> 00:38:29,500
You'd always chat with me in my dreams.

370
